[src:active-filters/sallen-key-topology] An example of a non-unity-gain bandpass filter implemented with a VCVS filter is shown in Figure 5.
[src:active-filters/sallen-key-topology] Although it uses a different topology and an operational amplifier configured to provide non-unity-gain, it can be analyzed using similar methods as with the generic Sallen–Key topology.
